the code i m submitting detects:
1) English word
2) Numbers in word (there must be space b/w each word such as 'one thousand six')
3) Punctuation as special characters
4) Numbers
5) Date
6) Devnagari words
7) few colours(such as red, yellow, green etc)
8) Licence plate number (in format : ga 09 f 0270)
